          text: 'Generative search optimisation targets all major AI-generated answer surfaces: Google AI Overviews (appearing on Google Search for a growing proportion of queries), ChatGPT Search (OpenAI\'s search mode), Perplexity AI (a dedicated AI search engine with live web retrieval), Microsoft Copilot (Bing-powered AI answers), and Gemini (Google\'s conversational AI integrated with Search). Each platform has a distinct retrieval mechanism, which is why cross-platform optimisation is a core component of a complete generative search strategy.'
        }
